      '**Page-load warning toast for missing database migrations.** If your database is missing one of the SQL migrations needed for star buttons / family templates / delete protection, a yellow warning toast pops up the moment you open the Product List, in addition to the amber banner at the top. You can\'t miss it now.',
      '**Star button diagnostics carry over from v.46.** When you click the star and the underlying column is missing, you get a clear "Stars not yet enabled — run SQL migration v55.83-A.6.27.38" message — no more silent failures.',
      '**No SQL changes. No database changes. No backout risk.** Pure UI improvements.',
