      '**Add Product Line search now finds products by ANY word in any order.** Type "headliner brown leather BMW" and it pulls up the matching product. Type the design SKU directly and it finds it. Search now matches across: Quick Code, Design SKU, English + Arabic name, classification slug, every classification level by readable name (Family, Category, Grade, Construction, Backing, Color, Pattern, Spec, Origin — both English and Arabic labels), supplier, and notes. Multi-keyword + any order. Sorted by ⭐ featured first, then most-used.',
