      '**Visual cues for required fields.** Empty required fields show a red border. The Quantity in Kilos label flips from "(optional)" to "*" the moment you pick "kg" as the unit. Placeholders clearly say "required" so nobody can miss it.',
      '**Submit-time validation catches everything.** If you try to submit a receipt missing UoM, Release #, Roll Count, or (when UoM=kg) Quantity in Kilos, you get a clear "Line N: <field> is required" alert before anything saves. Existing variance-reason and roll count validation still applies.',
